    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "At approximately 1:30 P.M., October 16, 1950, while working at Blair Gate, I saw",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "an object in the air over K-25 traveling in a northeast direction from the southwest.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "It was traveling in a straight line and going very fast. The object was white or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "silvery in color and round like a ball and was about the size of a baseball as seen",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "at the distance it was from me. It seemed to be very high.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "At exactly 2\"55 P.M., October 16, 1950, this object reappeared from the northeast",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "at a considerably lower altitude and traveling a lot slower than before. It stopped",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "a car that was coming in the gate in order to have witnesses to what I saw. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "occupants of the car were Troopers Lendelle Clark and Hank N. Briggs going in to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "work. I pointed out the object to Troopers Clark and Briggs and we watched the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "object for several minutes. This object was slowly circling in a wide circle",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "and spinning very fast, that is, the object itself was spinning around and around.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "The object drifted toward the southwest and in just a few minutes it reappeared at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "a very high altitude going back into the northeast and going very fast. We",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "watched the object disappear into the northeast.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "This information was phoned in to Headquarters immediately by the undersigned. About",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "fifteen minutes after the object disappeared into the northeast, an F-82 Fighter",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "plane showed up in the area where the object was last seen but appeared to be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "thousands of feet lower than the object which Troopers Clark, Briggs, and the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "undersigned saw and reported.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "status": "blank"
